<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/resources/do_circle.svg">
    <title>DO :: 얼굴 등록</title>

    <meta name="title" content="DO">
    <meta name="description" content="논산대건고등학교 인트라넷 DO 입니다.">
    <meta property="og:title" content="DO">
    <meta property="og:description" content="논산대건고등학교 인트라넷 DO 입니다.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="/resources/og_image.png">
    <meta property="og:url" content="v5.dghs.site">

    <!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-KCZ7CDL7SL"></script>
    <script> window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || []; function gtag() { dataLayer.push(arguments); } gtag('js', new Date()); gtag('config', 'G-KCZ7CDL7SL'); 
    </script>

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="/views/js/pay-facesign.js"></script>
    <script>
        function setVh() {
            let vh = window.innerHeight * 0.01;
            document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--vh', `${vh}px`);
        }

        window.addEventListener('resize', setVh);
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', setVh);
        setVh();
    </script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/views/css/defalut.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="
        relative flex flex-col items-center justify-start
        overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-hidden
        gap-5 text-[20px] text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 w-full full-height">

        <div id="TOP_AREA" class="
            relative flex justify-start items-end
            flex-row flex-nowrap 
            flex-grow-0 flex-shrink-0 basis-auto
            h-[80px] max-w-[600px] 
            overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-hidden
            px-[20px]
            w-full sm:w-[100%] md:w-[70%] lg:w-[50%]">
            <img src="/resources/do_logo.png" width="32" height="32" onclick="location.href='/'">
        </div>

        <div id="CONTENT_AREA" class="
            relative flex flex-col justify-start items-start
            flex-nowrap 
            flex-grow flex-shrink-0 basis-0
            h-[1fr] max-w-[600px]
            overflow-x-auto overflow-y-auto
            px-[20px] space-y-5
            w-full sm:w-[100%] md:w-[70%] lg:w-[50%]">
            <div id="intro_box" class="space-y-1">
                <p class="text-[22px] sm:text-[24px] text-gray-800 pretendard-700">
                    얼굴 등록을 하려면 동의해주세요.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[18px] sm:text-[20px] text-gray-700 pretendard-500">
                    필요한 부분만 추렸어요.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div id="agree_box" class="flex flex-row items-center justify-start w-full h-[50px] p-3 space-x-2 rounded-lg bg-white">
                <div>
                    <label>
                        <input id="agree_input" type="checkbox" class="hidden peer" />
                        <span class="cursor-pointer text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-500 peer-checked:text-blue-500">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path d="m10.4099 17.8538c-.3393 0-.67866-.1131-.90488-.4524l-5.20306-5.2031c-.56556-.5655-.56556-1.3573 0-1.9228.56555-.56559 1.35732-.56559 1.92287 0l4.18507 4.185 7.4653-7.46523c.5655-.56555 1.3573-.56555 1.9228 0 .5656.56555.5656 1.35732 0 1.92287l-8.3701 8.37016c-.3393.4524-.6787.5655-1.018.5655z"
                                    fill="currentColor" />
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                    </label>
                </div>
            
                <div class="flex-1 w-0 overflow-hidden">
                    <span class="block truncate text-[16px] md:text-[18px] text-gray-600 pretendard-500">
                        <span class="text-[16px] md:text-[18px] text-blue-500 pretendard-600">필수</span>
                        안면정보(민감정보) 수집 및 이용 동의
                    </span>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <span class="cursor-pointer rounded-lg px-2 text-[14px] md:text-[16px] text-gray-400 pretendard-600 transition-all duration-100 ease-in-out hover:text-gray-500"
                        onclick="location.href='/pay/facesign-privacy'">></span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="BOTTOM_AREA" class="
            relative flex flex-col justify-end items-start
            flex-nowrap 
            flex-grow-0 flex-shrink-0 basis-auto
            h-[100px] max-w-[600px]
            overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-hidden
            px-[20px] pb-[50px] space-y-5
            w-full sm:w-[100%] md:w-[70%] lg:w-[50%]">
            <button class="
                w-[100%] h-[48px] text-[18px] rounded-[18px] bg-blue-600
                text-white text-center pretendard-500
                sm:h-[54px] sm:text-[20px]
                active:scale-95 hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all duration-100 ease-in-out"
                onclick="agree()">
                다음
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>